{"tid":2140054,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"咪再follow埋啲濕鳩大陸語錄 支持本地製作啦 中意貓入 中意語錄入","createTime":"2020-08-04T17:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T08:12:54.000Z","uid":200667,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d017758ce47df60940f95d42624c1e83bc51cabd","tid":2140054,"uid":200667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"本身係個比較多愁善感嘅人 成日會諗埋好多少矯情嘅句子<br />\n又中意畫畫<br />\n見依家好興語錄 圖文個啲 <br />\n所以開左個page<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n專係圖文同語錄製作 奈何接觸唔到好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望<strong>連登界嘅各位</strong>如果中意呢類型嘅嘢 就follow下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>@catisstrange</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">唔好睇咁多大陸個啲版本啦 睇壞腦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 我有用vpn的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9nkXyJG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9nkXyJG.png&h=20b3c984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qxQTRvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqxQTRvm.jpg&h=d826a887&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dwoRDam.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdwoRDam.jpg&h=eafbdefd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKDBPg2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKDBPg2.jpg&h=ac50f0be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep899g2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp899g2.jpg&h=005e753c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwOx63J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwOx63J.jpg&h=cdada814&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kY3qHB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkY3qHB4.jpg&h=38